    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      World news story
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Information and events for British citizens in Denmark
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The British Embassy in Copenhagen has been holding meetings across Denmark to update UK nationals working and living in the country and answering their questions regarding Britain's exit from the European Union. </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
