<div class="call-to-action">
<p>Visit our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/living-in-denmark" class="govuk-link">Living in Denmark Guide</a> for practical information and the latest from the Danish government. You can receive email alerts whenever the guide is updated by <a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup/?topic=/world/living-in-denmark" class="govuk-link">signing up</a>.</p>
</div>

<p>To receive updates on what our team is up to, make sure to follow us on <a rel="external" href="https://www.facebook.com/britishembassycopenhagen/?ref=bookmarks" class="govuk-link">Facebook</a> and <a rel="external" href="https://www.twitter.com/UKinDenmark" class="govuk-link">Twitter</a></p>

