<p>For questions concerning your rights as a UK national in Denmark <a href="https://www.gov.uk/world/organisations/british-embassy-copenhagen" class="govuk-link">contact us</a>. If you have any suggestions for other towns and places that could host our citizens outreach meeting, <a href="mailto:events.copenhagen@fco.gov.uk" class="govuk-link">please email us</a></p>

<p>For press enquiries, <a href="mailto:lars.muller@fco.gov.uk" class="govuk-link">contact us</a></p>

